default.text:
'Sound-Powered Telephone'

In Referendum 196 the community voted on whether to open a HRMP channel between Parallel Heiko and Statemine (2nd attempt after Referendum 188 did not pass). This would allow the two parachains to communicate with one another.

Artist: @kseniashikh
